===Noun===
'''fool''' (plural: [[fools]])

#A person with poor judgment or little intelligence.
#A [[jester]], a person whose role was to entertain a [[sovereign]] and the [[court]].
#A type of [[dessert]] made of [[purée]]d fruit and [[custard]] or [[cream]].

====Synonyms====
*(''person with poor judgement''): ''See'' [[WikiSaurus:fool]]
*(''person who entertained a sovereign''): [[jester]], [[joker]]
*(''person who talks alot of nonsense''): [[gobshite]]

